# SalesVault Mobile App — Walkthrough

## Summary
Built a complete React Native Expo mobile app with **30+ files**, **8 feature modules**, role-adaptive navigation, JWT auth with secure storage, and a modern minimalist design system.

**TypeScript: ✅ Zero errors** | **Metro: ✅ 1307 modules bundled**

---

## Architecture

```
mobile-app/
├── app/
│   ├── _layout.tsx              ← Root: auth guard, splash, status bar
│   ├── (auth)/
│   │   ├── _layout.tsx          ← Auth stack (headerless)
│   │   └── login.tsx            ← Login (email/password, error handling)
│   └── (app)/
│       ├── _layout.tsx          ← Bottom tabs (role-adaptive)
│       ├── index.tsx            ← Dashboard (admin/salesperson)
│       ├── products/            ← List, detail, create
│       ├── sales/               ← List, create, detail
│       ├── activity/            ← Audit log feed
│       ├── profile/             ← Profile, logout, admin menus
│       ├── stock/               ← Stock levels, assign
│       ├── warehouses/          ← Warehouse list
│       └── users/               ← User list, create (admin)
├── src/
│   ├── constants/
│   │   ├── theme.ts             ← Design tokens (colors, spacing, shadows)
│   │   └── api.ts               ← API endpoints
│   ├── services/
│   │   ├── api.ts               ← Axios + JWT interceptor + refresh queue
│   │   └── auth.ts              ← expo-secure-store token management
│   ├── stores/
│   │   └── auth-store.ts        ← Zustand (login, logout, initialize)
│   └── components/ui/
│       ├── Button.tsx            ← 4 variants, haptic, loading
│       ├── Input.tsx             ← Label, error, password toggle
│       ├── Card.tsx              ← Elevated surface
│       ├── Badge.tsx             ← Status badges
│       └── StatCard.tsx          ← Dashboard metrics
```

---

## Key Features

| Feature | Implementation |
|---------|---------------|
| **Auth Guard** | Root layout checks `isAuthenticated`, redirects to login or app |
| **Secure Tokens** | `expo-secure-store` — encrypted on device |
| **Auto Refresh** | 401 interceptor with queued retry (no race conditions) |
| **Role-Adaptive Tabs** | Activity tab hidden for salesperson; Stock/Users via Profile menu |
| **Dashboard** | Admin: stats + top salespersons + activity. Salesperson: my stats |
| **Pull-to-Refresh** | Every list screen |
| **Pagination** | Products, Sales, Users (load more on scroll) |
| **Haptic Feedback** | Buttons use `expo-haptics` |
| **Dark/Light Mode** | Full theme support via `useColorScheme()` |
| **Idempotency** | Auto-generated key on sale creation |

