---

## How to Run

```bash
cd mobile-app
npx expo start
```

> Scan QR with Expo Go, or press `w` for web, `a` for Android emulator.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> For physical device testing, update `API_BASE_URL` in [src/constants/api.ts](file:///c:/Users/mrnad/OneDrive/Desktop/salesvault-stock-management%20system/mobile-app/src/constants/api.ts) to your machine's IP address.
